---
title: Roasted Chicken Dinner with Creamy Mash, Root Veg and Pull-Apart Cheesy Bread
description: Crispy, juicy roasted chicken is turned up with a best-kept Aussi secret: chicken salt! Not forgetting the seemingly simple pan-gravy – you'll want to sop up every last drop with the creamy mash or cheese-stuffed pull-apart bread. This is not your average chicken dinner!
